1
00:00:35,930 --> 00:00:38,560
=Angels and Guards=

2
00:00:38,560 --> 00:00:41,310
=Episode 29=

3
00:01:05,166 --> 00:01:06,750
What treasure is this?

4
00:01:07,000 --> 00:01:08,041
Such a large chest.

5
00:01:08,041 --> 00:01:08,625
Good eye.

6
00:01:08,625 --> 00:01:09,500
Is it for us?

7
00:01:09,916 --> 00:01:10,666
Don't ask.

8
00:01:12,958 --> 00:01:13,541
Pour the wine.

9
00:01:17,708 --> 00:01:20,500
You want the post
of Henan Provincial Commissioner?

10
00:01:21,083 --> 00:01:23,250
Henan is Prince Fu's fief.

11
00:01:23,625 --> 00:01:25,250
I wish to serve in Henan

12
00:01:25,708 --> 00:01:27,375
and devote myself to His Highness.

13
00:01:28,541 --> 00:01:29,291
This is all?

14
00:01:29,416 --> 00:01:31,291
This is a gift for you, Mr. Gao.

15
00:01:31,708 --> 00:01:34,250
As for Prince Fu, His Highness
names his own price.

16
00:01:34,541 --> 00:01:35,625
Go prepare the money.

17
00:01:36,500 --> 00:01:37,375
Wait for my word.

18
00:01:44,750 --> 00:01:45,708
Hua, are you all right?

19
00:01:46,000 --> 00:01:46,875
I'm fine, Xintian.

20
00:01:47,625 --> 00:01:49,375
This place really is where power
and money trade hands.

21
00:01:50,041 --> 00:01:52,125
Prince Fu is selling offices
and building his own faction here.

22
00:01:52,625 --> 00:01:54,041
Hua, I found something too.

23
00:01:54,375 --> 00:01:56,125
Most of the people here were trafficked.

24
00:01:56,416 --> 00:01:58,375
They treat lives like dirt
and force women into prostitution.

25
00:01:59,875 --> 00:02:00,583
Right, Xintian.

26
00:02:01,583 --> 00:02:02,916
Did you find anything about Leng Xin?

27
00:02:03,791 --> 00:02:04,500
Hua,

28
00:02:04,625 --> 00:02:05,833
I asked many kitchen helpers,

29
00:02:05,958 --> 00:02:06,958
but none of them knew him.

30
00:02:19,791 --> 00:02:20,625
Ouch, it hurts!

31
00:02:21,375 --> 00:02:22,291
Xintian. It's me.

32
00:02:23,250 --> 00:02:24,125
Sorry, Taozi.

33
00:02:24,250 --> 00:02:24,583
Xintian.

34
00:02:24,708 --> 00:02:26,541
Didn't you tell me to eat drumsticks
tonight?

35
00:02:27,375 --> 00:02:27,583
Right.

36
00:02:28,166 --> 00:02:29,208
Come. Sit.

37
00:02:30,208 --> 00:02:30,833
I will get one for you.

38
00:02:30,958 --> 00:02:31,250
Okay.

39
00:02:42,416 --> 00:02:43,916
Xintian, you know martial arts?

40
00:02:45,833 --> 00:02:46,250
I...

41
00:02:47,375 --> 00:02:48,916
No, I don't. Don't say that.

42
00:02:49,666 --> 00:02:50,541
Don't worry.

43
00:02:50,958 --> 00:02:52,500
You are the kindest person to me
in all of Meizhen House.

44
00:02:52,791 --> 00:02:53,958
I will treat you like my real sister.

45
00:02:55,541 --> 00:02:57,708
Then from now on,
you are my real little sister.

46
00:03:01,916 --> 00:03:02,708
Ms. Jiang, spare me!

47
00:03:02,708 --> 00:03:03,791
You think I can't handle you?

48
00:03:03,791 --> 00:03:04,375
Ms. Jiang, spare me!

49
00:03:04,375 --> 00:03:05,958
I will never do it again!

50
00:03:06,458 --> 00:03:07,791
I will beat you to death. Believe me?

51
00:03:08,291 --> 00:03:09,708
Do you know who Mr. Liu is?

52
00:03:10,166 --> 00:03:12,125
Do you know what happens
when you offend him?

53
00:03:12,416 --> 00:03:13,083
Do you?

54
00:03:13,708 --> 00:03:14,250
Ms. Jiang.

55
00:03:14,583 --> 00:03:15,583
Ms. Jiang.

56
00:03:18,791 --> 00:03:19,291
Ms. Jiang.

57
00:03:21,375 --> 00:03:21,791
Ms. Jiang.

58
00:03:22,333 --> 00:03:23,583
These are fresh honey peaches
picked today.

59
00:03:23,916 --> 00:03:24,750
I washed them with well water.

60
00:03:25,083 --> 00:03:25,833
Have a taste.

61
00:03:27,125 --> 00:03:28,291
You know how to please people.

62
00:03:29,916 --> 00:03:31,208
You two should have one too.

63
00:03:33,916 --> 00:03:34,416
Thanks.

64
00:03:37,041 --> 00:03:37,541
Let's go.

65
00:03:39,708 --> 00:03:41,000
Act up again,

66
00:03:41,125 --> 00:03:42,625
and a beating will be the least of it.

67
00:03:45,125 --> 00:03:45,583
Taozi.

68
00:03:46,583 --> 00:03:47,041
Come here.

69
00:03:55,125 --> 00:03:55,916
Taozi.

70
00:03:56,333 --> 00:03:57,666
If you get hungry tonight,

71
00:03:57,958 --> 00:03:59,166
sneak into the kitchen.

72
00:03:59,833 --> 00:04:00,500
I will save you a drumstick.

73
00:04:03,125 --> 00:04:03,833
Taozi,

74
00:04:04,625 --> 00:04:06,125
how did you end up at Meizhen House?

75
00:04:08,916 --> 00:04:09,250
I...

76
00:04:10,083 --> 00:04:12,291
I was abducted by traffickers.

77
00:04:13,625 --> 00:04:15,000
I missed home and tried to run,

78
00:04:15,750 --> 00:04:18,458
but every man in Meizhen House
knows martial arts.

79
00:04:18,458 --> 00:04:19,250
I couldn't escape.

80
00:04:20,083 --> 00:04:20,583
Before,

81
00:04:21,250 --> 00:04:22,666
one girl in my room ran away.

82
00:04:23,208 --> 00:04:24,375
They caught her and brought her back.

83
00:04:25,416 --> 00:04:27,500
After that, no one ever saw her again.

84
00:04:28,333 --> 00:04:29,791
So I became even more afraid to run.

85
00:04:31,583 --> 00:04:32,541
So that's what happened.

86
00:04:38,333 --> 00:04:38,875
Beiming, look.

87
00:04:39,625 --> 00:04:40,708
Such a luxurious carriage...

88
00:04:40,833 --> 00:04:42,083
What is it doing in the middle
of nowhere?

89
00:05:01,083 --> 00:05:01,583
Zheng Lun.

90
00:05:02,750 --> 00:05:03,625
Who did this to you?

91
00:05:05,458 --> 00:05:06,333
Gao Tianxi.

92
00:05:09,791 --> 00:05:11,666
I served him for so many years,

93
00:05:11,875 --> 00:05:12,458
yet he

94
00:05:13,291 --> 00:05:14,833
killed my whole family.

95
00:05:16,833 --> 00:05:17,375
Stop talking.

96
00:05:17,916 --> 00:05:18,666
I will take you to a doctor.

97
00:05:19,208 --> 00:05:19,708
No.

98
00:05:20,583 --> 00:05:21,375
Meizhen House

99
00:05:21,958 --> 00:05:25,125
is where Prince Fu plants his faction

100
00:05:26,833 --> 00:05:29,416
and eliminates his enemies.

101
00:05:30,958 --> 00:05:31,791
Prince Fu

102
00:05:32,208 --> 00:05:34,125
uses money and women

103
00:05:35,291 --> 00:05:36,833
to control court officials.

104
00:05:37,250 --> 00:05:40,958
His goal is to bring down
the Crown Prince,

105
00:05:41,250 --> 00:05:41,875
then

106
00:05:42,541 --> 00:05:44,875
seize the throne.

107
00:06:00,750 --> 00:06:01,958
There you are.

108
00:06:02,041 --> 00:06:03,083
I have been looking everywhere.

109
00:06:04,083 --> 00:06:04,666
Ms. Jiang.

110
00:06:06,708 --> 00:06:07,583
Were you looking for me?

111
00:06:07,958 --> 00:06:09,666
Good. You are both here.

112
00:06:09,791 --> 00:06:10,583
Listen up.

113
00:06:10,666 --> 00:06:11,583
There is a curfew tonight.

114
00:06:13,208 --> 00:06:14,291
What is a curfew?

115
00:06:14,458 --> 00:06:16,333
A curfew means exactly
what it sounds like.

116
00:06:16,458 --> 00:06:18,125
No business tonight.

117
00:06:18,916 --> 00:06:19,916
After dark,

118
00:06:19,916 --> 00:06:21,875
everyone in this house,

119
00:06:21,875 --> 00:06:24,166
no matter who they are,
stays in their room.

120
00:06:24,458 --> 00:06:25,750
If anything happens,

121
00:06:25,875 --> 00:06:27,791
don't say I didn't warn you.

122
00:06:30,083 --> 00:06:31,000
Be careful.

123
00:06:39,250 --> 00:06:40,666
Hua. Xintian.

124
00:06:41,083 --> 00:06:41,625
Taozi.

125
00:06:42,833 --> 00:06:45,083
Does this happen every time

126
00:06:46,708 --> 00:06:47,375
an important guest comes?

127
00:06:48,583 --> 00:06:49,250
Yes.

128
00:06:50,375 --> 00:06:52,333
It happens once a month,
at the end of the month.

129
00:06:53,041 --> 00:06:54,500
We are locked in our rooms

130
00:06:54,625 --> 00:06:55,750
and forbidden to wander around.

131
00:06:56,500 --> 00:06:58,583
Then, Manager Gao picks one of the girls

132
00:06:58,583 --> 00:06:59,791
to serve the important guest.

133
00:07:00,875 --> 00:07:01,958
And the girl he picks

134
00:07:03,166 --> 00:07:04,500
is gone by the next morning.

135
00:07:04,916 --> 00:07:06,000
No one ever sees her again.

136
00:07:09,500 --> 00:07:11,500
(Account Book)
Master, the last month's account book.

137
00:07:16,041 --> 00:07:18,166
How is the matter arranged?

138
00:07:19,625 --> 00:07:20,583
For an assassination,

139
00:07:21,041 --> 00:07:23,166
we need someone absolutely reliable.

140
00:07:24,333 --> 00:07:26,333
Leng Xin must be handled in secret.

141
00:07:27,500 --> 00:07:28,125
It's done.

142
00:07:28,416 --> 00:07:28,875
Who's there?

143
00:07:34,083 --> 00:07:34,833
Assassin!

144
00:07:36,500 --> 00:07:38,208
Xintian, we are exposed. Run!

145
00:07:41,416 --> 00:07:41,875
Stop!

146
00:07:43,333 --> 00:07:43,833
Don't run!

147
00:07:50,500 --> 00:07:50,875
Run!

148
00:07:52,208 --> 00:07:52,625
Don't run!

149
00:07:53,500 --> 00:07:54,041
Stop!

150
00:08:02,708 --> 00:08:03,583
Who sent you?

151
00:08:04,708 --> 00:08:05,291
Hua.

152
00:08:05,958 --> 00:08:06,708
Xintian, go!

153
00:08:19,333 --> 00:08:20,125
Darn it!

154
00:08:26,375 --> 00:08:26,833
All right.

155
00:08:29,333 --> 00:08:29,833
Tell me.

156
00:08:30,666 --> 00:08:31,875
Who sent you here?

157
00:08:32,583 --> 00:08:33,625
Jinyiwei

158
00:08:34,416 --> 00:08:35,541
Northern Bureau.

159
00:08:35,666 --> 00:08:36,291
Shut up!

160
00:08:36,625 --> 00:08:37,458
Tell me the truth.

161
00:08:37,916 --> 00:08:39,291
The Crown Prince sent you, didn't he?

162
00:08:40,000 --> 00:08:41,125
What Crown Prince?

163
00:08:41,791 --> 00:08:42,833
I told you.

164
00:08:43,416 --> 00:08:46,416
Can't you understand my words?

165
00:08:49,375 --> 00:08:50,250
Still refusing to talk?

166
00:08:52,000 --> 00:08:53,833
Then let's make this hurt.

167
00:08:53,875 --> 00:08:55,291
Chili oil.

168
00:09:32,166 --> 00:09:33,041
Wake her with cold water.

169
00:09:33,250 --> 00:09:33,625
Yes.

170
00:10:06,416 --> 00:10:07,791
Gao Tianxi.

171
00:10:08,708 --> 00:10:10,000
One day,

172
00:10:10,416 --> 00:10:12,583
I will make sure you die screaming.

173
00:10:16,583 --> 00:10:18,708
Then I will burn out your eyes first,

174
00:10:19,416 --> 00:10:20,833
then ruin that face of yours.

175
00:10:28,250 --> 00:10:28,708
Boss!

176
00:10:28,875 --> 00:10:29,750
Boss, bad news!

177
00:10:29,916 --> 00:10:31,000
A large force is outside.

178
00:10:31,166 --> 00:10:32,333
They have surrounded Meizhen House.

179
00:10:34,125 --> 00:10:35,291
Hide her!

180
00:10:35,666 --> 00:10:36,166
Yes!

181
00:10:51,791 --> 00:10:52,708
Chang Beiming.

182
00:10:53,208 --> 00:10:54,041
What is the meaning of this?

183
00:10:54,916 --> 00:10:55,791
Hand over Hua.

184
00:10:55,791 --> 00:10:56,458
Gao Tianxi.

185
00:10:56,875 --> 00:11:00,000
Hand over Hua Mange, Chief Squad Leader
of the Northern Bureau.

186
00:11:00,208 --> 00:11:00,708
Or

187
00:11:01,458 --> 00:11:03,041
I will level Meizhen House.

188
00:11:04,166 --> 00:11:05,333
With just you?

189
00:11:06,375 --> 00:11:07,291
Add the three of us.

190
00:11:08,375 --> 00:11:09,000
Is that enough?

191
00:11:09,041 --> 00:11:10,000
Do you think

192
00:11:10,250 --> 00:11:11,375
this whole capital

193
00:11:11,375 --> 00:11:13,500
belongs to the Chang family?

194
00:11:14,208 --> 00:11:15,125
Don't forget,

195
00:11:15,875 --> 00:11:18,875
even the Jinyiwei are split
between North and South.

196
00:11:19,625 --> 00:11:20,958
Young masters,

197
00:11:21,250 --> 00:11:22,375
you bring armed men here

198
00:11:22,791 --> 00:11:24,083
without cause or warrant.

199
00:11:24,750 --> 00:11:27,000
Don't you fear Prince Fu's wrath?

200
00:11:28,458 --> 00:11:29,583
So, you are saying

201
00:11:30,083 --> 00:11:31,333
the power behind Meizhen House

202
00:11:32,500 --> 00:11:33,833
is Prince Fu himself?

203
00:11:34,916 --> 00:11:35,875
If we find her here,

204
00:11:36,125 --> 00:11:36,916
the law stands above all.

205
00:11:37,291 --> 00:11:38,125
Prince Fu doesn't matter.

206
00:11:38,416 --> 00:11:39,541
You can't search
just because you say so.

207
00:11:39,583 --> 00:11:41,125
What do you take Meizhen House for?

208
00:11:41,458 --> 00:11:43,583
Meizhen House is not
a government office.

209
00:11:43,583 --> 00:11:44,958
If we want to search it, we search it.

210
00:11:45,083 --> 00:11:47,166
Do we need Cabinet approval too?

211
00:11:47,250 --> 00:11:49,333
Besides, the Eastern Depot
may act first and report later.

212
00:11:50,375 --> 00:11:52,083
(Prince Fu)
Prince Fu's imperial gold token is here.

213
00:11:52,291 --> 00:11:53,208
Who dares defy it?

214
00:12:03,416 --> 00:12:04,416
Bring forth the Founding Emperor's

215
00:12:04,791 --> 00:12:06,000
Iron Certificate!

216
00:12:35,625 --> 00:12:36,708
We pay our respects
to the Founding Emperor.

217
00:12:38,000 --> 00:12:40,000
We pay our respects
to the Founding Emperor.

218
00:12:41,875 --> 00:12:42,541
Chang Beiming.

219
00:12:45,166 --> 00:12:47,375
Since you have brought
the Iron Certificate,

220
00:12:47,833 --> 00:12:49,083
I have nothing more to say.

221
00:12:50,208 --> 00:12:51,291
If you find nothing,

222
00:12:52,708 --> 00:12:53,166
you

223
00:12:54,416 --> 00:12:55,958
will answer to Prince Fu.

224
00:12:56,125 --> 00:12:57,333
What answer do you want?

225
00:13:08,791 --> 00:13:09,916
You want an answer?

226
00:13:10,416 --> 00:13:11,750
How about I give you one?

227
00:13:13,666 --> 00:13:14,458
Gao Tianxi.

228
00:13:15,125 --> 00:13:17,500
Have you grown that bold?

229
00:13:18,416 --> 00:13:20,375
You dare lay hands
on my Northern Bureau officer?

230
00:13:20,666 --> 00:13:22,166
Every Jinyiwei here

231
00:13:22,500 --> 00:13:23,666
answers only to the Emperor.

232
00:13:24,208 --> 00:13:25,375
Let's see who dares make a move.

233
00:13:27,083 --> 00:13:27,583
Mr. Zhang.

234
00:13:28,333 --> 00:13:29,416
I mean no disrespect.

235
00:13:30,125 --> 00:13:32,208
But if they find nothing,

236
00:13:32,541 --> 00:13:33,000
will she

237
00:13:33,666 --> 00:13:35,083
dare answer to Prince Fu

238
00:13:35,375 --> 00:13:36,375
with her life?

239
00:13:44,875 --> 00:13:45,541
Bingfan.

240
00:13:49,708 --> 00:13:50,166
Search this place!

241
00:13:55,333 --> 00:13:56,666
Beiming and I will search below for Hua.

242
00:13:56,958 --> 00:13:57,666
You search up here.

243
00:14:00,625 --> 00:14:02,166
Xintian. Xintian.

244
00:14:02,666 --> 00:14:03,083
Xintian.

245
00:14:03,416 --> 00:14:03,958
Taozi.

246
00:14:09,125 --> 00:14:10,333
Do you know where Hua is being held?

247
00:14:10,833 --> 00:14:12,166
Anyone who breaks the rules here

248
00:14:12,416 --> 00:14:13,916
is taken to the dungeon and tortured.

249
00:14:14,500 --> 00:14:15,416
They locked me there once.

250
00:14:15,666 --> 00:14:16,333
I can take you.

251
00:14:17,416 --> 00:14:19,750
Hua! Hua!

252
00:14:20,333 --> 00:14:20,666
Hua!

253
00:14:21,416 --> 00:14:22,000
Hua!

254
00:14:22,416 --> 00:14:24,625
Please save us!

255
00:14:25,208 --> 00:14:26,041
Please!

256
00:14:26,041 --> 00:14:26,916
Hurry. Get them out!

257
00:14:26,916 --> 00:14:27,416
Yes!

258
00:14:27,416 --> 00:14:28,208
Who are these girls?

259
00:14:28,208 --> 00:14:29,250
They were all abducted.

260
00:14:31,291 --> 00:14:32,375
Thank you.

261
00:14:36,333 --> 00:14:37,166
This could

262
00:14:38,083 --> 00:14:39,458
go all the way to the throne.

263
00:14:40,375 --> 00:14:41,458
Are you sure this will work?

264
00:14:42,875 --> 00:14:43,583
Not at all.

265
00:14:44,541 --> 00:14:45,750
But neither of us has a way out.

266
00:14:47,291 --> 00:14:48,208
Bold.

267
00:14:57,000 --> 00:14:57,916
This is the torture room.

268
00:14:58,458 --> 00:15:00,416
They punish rule-breakers here.

269
00:15:01,291 --> 00:15:02,500
Hua was tortured here?

270
00:15:04,083 --> 00:15:04,541
Hua!

271
00:15:05,416 --> 00:15:05,958
Hua!

272
00:15:21,916 --> 00:15:23,125
Bingfan, you found nothing?

273
00:15:26,208 --> 00:15:27,875
Chang Beiming, where is the woman
you came for?

274
00:15:28,291 --> 00:15:29,083
You can't find her, can you?

275
00:15:30,750 --> 00:15:33,166
This is clearly a trumped-up charge.

276
00:15:33,666 --> 00:15:35,458
Seize Shen Bingfan.

277
00:15:35,833 --> 00:15:36,291
Guards!

278
00:15:36,750 --> 00:15:37,750
Take her!

279
00:15:38,375 --> 00:15:38,583
Yes!

280
00:15:38,583 --> 00:15:39,583
Gao Tianxi, you scum!

281
00:15:47,833 --> 00:15:49,166
Gao Tianxi, I will kill you!

282
00:15:51,708 --> 00:15:52,166
Duoyu.

283
00:15:52,500 --> 00:15:52,833
Xintian.

284
00:15:53,291 --> 00:15:54,333
Find a doctor for Hua. Now!

285
00:15:54,625 --> 00:15:55,250
Go!

286
00:15:55,250 --> 00:15:55,708
Go!

287
00:15:57,666 --> 00:15:58,208
You monster!

288
00:15:58,375 --> 00:15:59,125
I will kill you!

289
00:15:59,416 --> 00:15:59,833
Bingfan.

290
00:16:00,125 --> 00:16:00,458
Calm down.

291
00:16:14,458 --> 00:16:15,416
Take him alive!

292
00:16:50,666 --> 00:16:52,291
Gao Tianxi deceived me.

293
00:16:52,666 --> 00:16:53,875
I had no idea

294
00:16:54,291 --> 00:16:55,416
he had taken someone
from the Northern Bureau.

295
00:16:57,208 --> 00:16:59,166
A man should choose a side,
not bend with the wind.

296
00:17:01,083 --> 00:17:02,666
You saw what happened to him.

297
00:17:07,291 --> 00:17:08,958
All Jinyiwei, hear my order!

298
00:17:10,208 --> 00:17:10,666
Yes!

299
00:17:10,958 --> 00:17:12,750
Seal off Meizhen House.

300
00:17:13,416 --> 00:17:14,000
Yes!

301
00:17:23,666 --> 00:17:25,333
Baihu Shen, all the enforcers
have been captured.

302
00:17:26,541 --> 00:17:26,916
Yes.

303
00:17:27,625 --> 00:17:28,041
Go!

304
00:17:29,666 --> 00:17:31,500
Bingfan, this is Taozi.

305
00:17:31,916 --> 00:17:33,875
Without her, we couldn't
have saved Hua today.

306
00:17:35,083 --> 00:17:35,500
Thank you.

307
00:17:36,541 --> 00:17:37,083
It's nothing.

308
00:17:37,583 --> 00:17:39,083
Don't be afraid, Taozi.

309
00:17:39,958 --> 00:17:41,083
Bingfan is like a sister to me.

310
00:17:41,541 --> 00:17:42,250
She is very kind.

311
00:17:43,708 --> 00:17:44,291
Bingfan.

312
00:17:45,666 --> 00:17:46,083
Xintian.

313
00:17:46,500 --> 00:17:48,166
Settle these girls
at the Northern Bureau for now.

314
00:17:48,666 --> 00:17:49,791
We may need their testimony later.

315
00:17:50,875 --> 00:17:51,416
Baihu Shen.

316
00:17:53,625 --> 00:17:55,291
(Account Book)
Baihu Shen, we found many account books.

317
00:17:56,083 --> 00:17:57,250
These are key pieces of evidence.

318
00:17:57,416 --> 00:17:58,000
Seal and store them.

319
00:17:58,125 --> 00:17:58,458
Yes.

320
00:18:03,270 --> 00:18:05,970
(Prince Fu)

321
00:18:09,291 --> 00:18:09,958
You have made quite a mess, huh?

322
00:18:11,166 --> 00:18:13,333
(Noble Consort Zheng)
Your Majesty, our son is young.

323
00:18:13,625 --> 00:18:14,750
He was misled by outsiders.

324
00:18:15,000 --> 00:18:17,041
He knew nothing about this.

325
00:18:17,500 --> 00:18:19,208
He was completely deceived.

326
00:18:19,500 --> 00:18:20,625
Please see the truth, Your Majesty.

327
00:18:21,416 --> 00:18:22,416
Yes. Father.

328
00:18:22,708 --> 00:18:24,000
A prince of the blood,

329
00:18:24,833 --> 00:18:26,208
scrambling for profit with commoners.

330
00:18:26,583 --> 00:18:27,625
How impressive.

331
00:18:43,520 --> 00:18:46,690
♪Because you once entered my dreams♪

332
00:18:47,060 --> 00:18:50,440
♪Truth and illusion blur in wine♪

333
00:18:50,690 --> 00:18:53,690
♪My heart drifted lost♪

334
00:18:53,690 --> 00:18:57,100
♪Yet found you in the crowd♪

335
00:18:58,190 --> 00:19:01,400
♪My blood still burns
as the world surges♪

336
00:19:01,810 --> 00:19:05,150
♪The land is fair, and you are free♪

337
00:19:05,730 --> 00:19:07,940
♪Sword drawn, lost in obsession♪

338
00:19:07,940 --> 00:19:11,980
♪I've softly let it go♪

339
00:19:11,980 --> 00:19:15,850
♪The vow you made was true♪

340
00:19:15,850 --> 00:19:19,600
♪Yet like clouds, it stops for no one♪

341
00:19:19,900 --> 00:19:21,810
♪Put away those dreamlike words♪

342
00:19:21,810 --> 00:19:26,350
♪And forget at world's end♪

343
00:19:26,650 --> 00:19:28,150
♪Embracing memory♪

344
00:19:28,150 --> 00:19:30,520
♪Through blossoms and dreams♪

345
00:19:30,520 --> 00:19:34,400
♪You hide in the crowd, silent♪

346
00:19:34,400 --> 00:19:36,730
♪I wish to let it pass♪

347
00:19:36,730 --> 00:19:41,730
♪And run toward this vast life♪

